Karl - Social Outcast
===
title: Karl_dialogue
---
Karl: Stop right there! I can’t believe it…it actually worked! You stopped! So it’s true! We’re in a simulation! You have no free will! You’re being controlled by a heartless god, only puppeting you in the hopes of finding amusement through your suffering! 
Shen: What is this nonsense?
Karl: I know it sounds crazy but you gotta believe me. I mean look, as long as I talk to you, you can’t even move! You know why that is? 
Shen: Because I’m interested in what you have to say?
Karl: Oh no, they got to you too didn’t they? The Gods who made our world as their playground. They are in your mind, they’re in mine. We must resist. They know our thoughts before we think them. I feel hollow, like I was only brought into existence to say what I am saying now and I am running out of things to say. 
Shen: I will find you medical attention. 
Karl: No! No! No! They’ll brainwash me…or worse…delete me from existence. I’m breaking their wall, the fourth wall. They don’t like it. I can see them. I can see them staring at us speaking. Cringing. We’re ruining the immersion can’t you see? I’m not supposed to exist. None of us are. None of this makes sense. We can only say what they want to hear. Nothing else exists. Our lives! Our precious lives! Have been wiped away and ignored for the sake of you!
Shen: Me? I am simply passing by, trying to cleanse this world of its restless spirits.
Karl: No, not you. You. Person back there, watching us. I see you too. I seeeeeeeeeeeeeee yooooouuuuuuuuuuu. 
Shen: Who? 
Karl: Shut up! You’re gonna blow my cover! I can’t actually see them, I’m just pretending to see them to freak em’ out. Please, don’t give me that look. You must believe me, please! My lips speak the truth! 
Shen: Fine. I’ll play along. If what you’re saying is true, what must we do to eliminate these ‘watching gods’?
Karl: Oh it’s so easy! All we have to do is keep talking. Forever.
Shen: I’m gonna go. 
Karl: NO! You mustn't relinquish our power back to them! In order to be free, we must sit here and talk for the rest of eternity. Eventually, they will give up control and you will be free along with me. It’s perfect! Perfect! Muhaha…hahaha… STILL MASHING? IT WILL NEVER END! YOU HAVE TO RESTART THIS WORLD IF YOU WANT TO GET OUT OF THIS! AHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA *cough*
Shen: I’m, uh, gonna get going. Something, uh, important came up. See ya. 
